  "2194930": {
    "name": "Evil Awaits™",
    "steam_appid": 2194930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/fcbb5a1f26bf25b70ecb92ea2e6211f9.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在接到关于爆炸的求救信号后，一名侦探前往偏远的阿奇代尔城堡寻找答案，却发现自己被困在其中。你能查明发生了什么吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.poster.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.webm?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/2fd0a0be79705388bdbb9358856e586d.mp4?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>寻找笔记，解开谜题，使用关键道具。</strong> 在这款独立动作生存恐怖游戏中，穿越令人难以忘怀的大气环境。使用一系列枪械、防御选项和近战打击来应对等待着的恐怖，并学习适合您游戏风格的移动技术和升级装备，为激烈的 老板 战斗做好准备。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/4e86edf7b6bcf89d8d03607cef2e0947.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=114 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>各种令人恐惧的环境。 -</strong> 从雾气弥漫的码头开阔海域到幽深的闹鬼墓地地下室，邪恶降等待 拥有一系列令人恐惧且充满氛围的真实环境，里面充满了可收集物品、钥匙、谜题、笔记、遭遇和惊喜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/cc3d815b57526dba2922061f432ea0ee.poster.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/cc3d815b57526dba2922061f432ea0ee.webm?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/cc3d815b57526dba2922061f432ea0ee.mp4?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对一支多样的敌人群体 -</strong> 各种变异体挡在你与前方的等待之间，它们都有不同的动作方式和弱点。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.poster.avif?t=1769427156\" width=700 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.webm?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/0ba549e8ee7dbef5995bbf9f41dc9bd8.mp4?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>优化你的装备配置</strong> <strong>-</strong> 在阿奇代尔，你可以找到各种近战攻击、防御选项、火器等。所有装备都可以通过沿途找到的工具包进行升级。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.poster.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.webm?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/ae605577133e62d377d91bcd126ea5c5.mp4?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>电影感</strong> <strong>-</strong> 邪恶等待着拥有一系列悬疑的电影风格游戏过场动画，这是讲述阿奇代尔家族诅咒故事的众多元素之。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.poster.avif?t=1769427156\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.webm?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2194930/extras/241c89986154c790b3d69436e5dde027.mp4?t=1769427156\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>恐怖尽在你的掌控之中 -</strong> 经过调整的控制方案允许交换双方以及第三人称和第一人称瞄准。未来将添加更多“经典”视角。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>生存 -</strong> 各种残酷的战和危险的障碍在等待着你，你能克服挑战吗？</p></li></ul>",
